wikipedia_page.main: Elliot Kebbie (born 11 September 1994) is an English former professional footballer of Sierra Leonean descent. A graduate of Leeds United's academy, he played as a defender or midfielder for  Atlético Madrid C, Rangers and Sandefjord and the England U-16 team.
